{"tid":1002843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"$2000/天  市場學碩士帶你了解港中大書院制","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:23:08.000Z","uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74c69e953dae4800d59e5a71d8d25279a65f612b","tid":1002843,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.8pig.com/journey/4916.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8pig.com%2Fjourney%2F4916.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6tUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=70a060df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8pig.com/journey/4916.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.8pig.com/road/u_16/4916/f3c12d7c0c4dbb12f42a60a260750b2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.8pig.com%2Froad%2Fu_16%2F4916%2Ff3c12d7c0c4dbb12f42a60a260750b2e.jpg&h=7a71b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n殘體唔好屌<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n市场学硕士带你了解港中大独一无二的书院制<br />\n中国香港 香港向导服务名校游学<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n达人简介<br />\n<br />\nHi我是Celine，与生俱来对这个世界始终保持着一种令人琢磨不透的热情与好奇，像新生儿般汲取着每一秒鲜活的生命跳动。也许是那一份可贵的纯真烂漫，也许是那一股让人震撼的求知欲与探索欲，我喜欢用独一无二的角度去诠释我眼中的世界。追求完美，考究细节，却又伴随着一丝随性。敏感细致，善于捕捉我眼中每一缕别样的风景，心灵栖息于撩动我心弦之处。喜欢分享，享受合作，挑战自我，不慌不忙地踏遍地球的每一角落。认真负责，幽默风趣，乐观开朗的正能量女孩。欢迎来港中大找我！//<br />\n<br />\n好有marketing頭腦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4445ddd18932dbe0063c3a6ce1a8283af92b626","tid":1002843,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"女神？？？<br />\n<br />\n港中大女神与你分享那些校园趣事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8pig.com/journey/4915.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8pig.com%2Fjourney%2F4915.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6tUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=724e9a05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8pig.com/journey/4915.html</a><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n哈喽，我是Rita，来自湖南的湘妹子，目前我在香港中文大学读社会服务管理学硕士。我本身喜欢有趣的事情，也想让自己变成一个有趣的人，在变得有趣这个方面或许你比我更有方法呢，那么请一定要跟我分享哟。当然，我也会把我认为有趣的事情告诉你的，在港大读书确实有很多趣事值得分享。另外我平时也喜欢摄影和旅行，并且是一位伪文艺咖，哈哈，还是一个超级话痨，不烦我的话就跟我一起来吧。CUHK真的很棒但是不来看看你怎么知道呀！<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.8pig.com/road/u_15/4915/4613500909feefdbeab1fc2998475bcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.8pig.com%2Froad%2Fu_15%2F4915%2F4613500909feefdbeab1fc2998475bcd.jpg&h=1e8a1944&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bd4c7be4e090133142b5536ef17fe02776537e7","tid":1002843,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"參觀hall room<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5911f7259cb7ce6868e01f0a3a01beb55e7f28d2","tid":1002843,"uid":164240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"2000/q都比多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1edbf080e04f80094afe605404d499ee9e8920b","tid":1002843,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"搞乜"},{"pid":"7be9a2dcc5415833f223a3ffa59d32c0067facd8","tid":1002843,"uid":228995,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"Btw <br />\n<br />\n有無法律撚？<br />\n<br />\n係咪算犯法？<br />\n<br />\nStudy visa 打工"},{"pid":"4dd7d16345bbd04cb99fa26995d7ca1adc3a4954","tid":1002843,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"收錢？違反逗留條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji